reviews.text: A good shopping mall near Chai wan MTR station in HongKong. Though it’s a small mall, you can experience some world-class brand here. You can also experience varieties of food and drink at different restaurant and food shops. Youth Square,  a nice accommodation is very close to it.
Good value for money, variety of goods available.
A lot of people in here. Very crowded.
Typical mini mall alongside residential area with little bit of everything
Not a tourist spot. Local medium level shopping centre.
